#: ../../source/api/actor_sensor.md:16
msgid "Circle Sensor"
msgstr ""

#: miniworlds.actors.sensors.circle_sensor.CircleSensor:1 of
msgid "A circular invisible sensor attached to another actor."
msgstr ""

#: miniworlds.actors.sensors.circle_sensor.CircleSensor:3 of
msgid ""
"`CircleSensor` creates a circular detection area around the parent actor. "
"Any actor that overlaps with this circle will be detected. The sensor itself "
"is invisible and never detects the parent actor."
msgstr ""

#: miniworlds.actors.sensors.circle_sensor.CircleSensor:7 of
msgid ""
"Use `actor.register_sensor(CircleSensor, distance=<pixels>)` to attach it."
msgstr ""

#: miniworlds.actors.sensors.circle_sensor.CircleSensor:9 of
msgid "The parent actor this sensor belongs to."
msgstr ""

#: miniworlds.actors.sensors.circle_sensor.CircleSensor:10 of
msgid "Radius of the circular detection area in pixels."
msgstr ""
